As president of the National Confederation of Transport (CNT) he has defended tax cuts for public transport corporations.<ref>{{cite web|title=Transporte urbano pode ter mais cortes de impostos|url=http://economia.estadao.com.br/noticias/geral,transporte-urbano-pode-ter-mais-cortes-de-impostos,148793e|work=[[O Estado de S. Paulo]]|accessdate=March 27, 2013}}</ref>
