The '''Greater Barrie Chamber of Commerce''' is a business organization first founded in [[Barrie]], [[Ontario]], in 1887. Representing the broad interests of over 1000 members, the Greater Barrie Chamber of Commerce serves its members with member-centred priorities and with an action plan that will benefit all local businesses.

